  "informal_statement": "The cross-product form of twice the signed area of a triangle equals its shoelace sum.",
  "informal_proof_idea": "Expand both cross products and the shoelace sum to the same polynomial; `ring`.",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem shoelace_identity (x1 y1 x2 y2 x3 y3 : ℝ) : (x2 - x1) * (y3 - y1) - (x3 - x1) * (y2 - y1) = x1 * y2 - x2 * y1 + (x2 * y3 - x3 * y2) + (x3 * y1 - x1 * y3)",
